13:
But as for me, Yahweh, I cry out to you to help me;
\q2 each morning I pray to you.
\q1

15:
All the time since I was young, I have suffered and have often almost died;
\q1 I am in despair because of enduring the terrible things that you have done to me.
\q1

16:
I feel that you have crushed me because of your being angry with me;
\q2 the terrible things that you are doing to me are almost destroying me.
\q1

17:
It is as though they surround me like a flood;
\q2 they are closing in on me from all sides.
\q1
